\/18\/angels-suhoor\/","url_meta":{"origin":34101,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Suhur: Allah and angels bless the pre-fasting meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 18, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah and His angels send blessings upon those who eat before fasting.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 3467 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9359,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/29\/reality-faith-love-others\/","url_meta":{"origin":34101,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Iman: No true faith until he loves others as himself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe servant does not attain the reality of faith until he loves for people what he loves for himself of goodness.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 235 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u06